TM TT LUN VN THC S
ti: S dng cc phng php phn loi t ng, x l nh s chn on bnh
trong lnh vc chn nui.
Tc gi lun vn: Th Nhm Kho 2012B.
Ngi hng dn: TS. Phm ng Hi , TS. Trnh Anh Phc
Ni dung tm tt:
a. L do la chn ti.
Trong lnh vc Nng nghip, chn nui l ngnh c v tr quan trng, c bit l
ngnh chn nui ln. Hin nay, chn nui ln cc h gia nh ang pht trin theo
hng tin b c v cht lng v s lng. Hu ht ngi chn nui bit p dng
mt s tin b khoa hc k thut vo chn nui nng cao nng sut cht lng sn
phm. Bn cnh nhng thnh cng th vn dch bnh vn thng xuyn xy ra
gy ra rt nhiu tn tht to ln, v th vic chn on ng bnh kp thi a ra
phng php phng v iu tr bnh l vic lm v cng quan trng. Mun vy ngi
chn nui khng th ch da vo kinh nghim bn thn m cn cn mt i ng
chuyn mn giu kinh nghim. Tuy nhin nc ta hin nay vn cn thiu cc i
ng chuyn mn ny. iu ny dn n cn tm hiu v a ra phng php thch hp
xy dng mt phn mm ng dng t ng nhm chn on bnh trong lnh vc
chn nui.
b. Mc ch nghin cu, i tng, phm vi p dng.
- Mc ch
- ti tp trung nghin cu v ng dng cc phng php x l v phn
loi nh s xy dng mt phn mm cho php chn on bnh ln qua
hnh nh chp.
- i tng, phm vi p dng
- ti tp trung tin hnh tm hiu cc biu hin trn da ca mt s loi
bnh hay gp ln.
- Nghin cu cc phng php x l nh s v phn loi nh t ng, sau khi
su tp cc d liu nh chp c th ln b bnh.
2
- nh gi kt qu, hiu qu ca cc phng php trn i vi vic chn on
bnh ln..
c. Cc ni dung chnh, ng gi mi.
Lun vn nghin cu v l thuyt ca cc phng php x l nh s v phn
loi t ng nhm thc hin xy dng phn mm ng dng gip chn on bnh qua
nh chp trong lnh vc chn nui. y cng chnh ng gp mi trong vic ng dng
Cng ngh thng tin vo pht trin ngnh chn nui ni ring v trong lnh vc nng
nghip ni chung.
d. Phng php nghin cu.
- Phng php thu thp d liu
- Phng php chun ha, phn tch v x l d liu.
- Phng php m un ho trong lp trnh.
e. Kt lun
V mt l thuyt lun vn trnh by c cc ni dung sau: gii thiu tng
quan cc phng php x l nh s nh: phn b c trng bin (Edge Histogram
Descriptor), tng quan mu sc (Color Correlograms), c trng kt cu s dng b
lc Gabor (Gabor Wavelets), Sift (Scale Invariant feature transform) l cc phng
php trch chn c trng cho nh s. Gii thiu tng quan phng php phn loi
nh s t ng SVM (Support Vector Machine). T a ra c phng hng
gii quyt bi ton chn on bnh ln qua hnh nh chp.
V mt thc nghim, lun vn thu c mt s kt qu sau: Xy dng, ci
t thnh cng bn gii thut x l nh s nhm trch chn cc c trng ca nh t
xy dng c b d liu hun luyn t cc nh chp v bnh ca ln.
Ci t thnh cng gii thut phn lp nh t ng SVM, kt qu thu c khi
phn loi chn on bnh ln mc kh.
